"1982.

14:23.412 --> 14:26.780
"Everglades National Park,
Florida.

14:26.782 --> 14:29.649
"Five mysterious lights dance
in the night sky.

14:29.651 --> 14:32.285
"A ray shoots down,
lifting the park ranger,

14:32.287 --> 14:35.872
"who, to be fair, was going
through a bad divorce

14:35.874 --> 14:40.126
and had a habit of lying
to get attention."

14:40.128 --> 14:42.045
I hate this job, Sandy!

14:42.047 --> 14:44.264
I went into journalism
to make a difference,

14:44.266 --> 14:46.800
but you have made
that impossible.

14:46.802 --> 14:48.718
You know, to be honest,
it hasn't been

14:48.720 --> 14:50.687
an easy couple months for me.
I've made mistakes.

14:50.689 --> 14:53.106
I've felt alone.
