14:53.108 --> 14:54.724
I didn't even know I had.

14:54.726 --> 14:56.943
So here's the deal:

14:56.945 --> 14:58.344
You're gonna get
back on air

14:58.346 --> 14:59.979
and count us
into a better year,

14:59.981 --> 15:04.567
because I just can't do
2011 anymore. You with me?

15:04.569 --> 15:06.986
He's not with me, is he?

15:13.305 --> 15:15.423
Anyway, Dad, where was I?

15:16.084 --> 15:17.368
You know what?
Fine, get out of here!

15:17.370 --> 15:19.620
We don't need ya!

15:21.456 --> 15:24.425
And why doesn't anybody
like these hats?

15:24.427 --> 15:28.429
I made these hats.

15:28.431 --> 15:30.097
It's because
they' wet, Doug.

15:30.099 --> 15:32.716
Why are they all wet?!

15:32.718 --> 15:34.835
Were those our last customers?

15:34.837 --> 15:36.854
Let me go check
the bathroom.

15:41.277 --> 15:43.527
You must be
from the escort service.

15:45.013 --> 15:50.734
The scenario is high school
wrestling match.

15:54.239 --> 15:55.188
Hello?

15:55.190 --> 15:57.791
