really want and you deserve it.

16:10.556 --> 16:12.556
Kevin, that's not how it works.

16:12.558 --> 16:13.974
Sounds like that's
your only choice.

16:13.976 --> 16:16.060
New York's a big city.

16:16.062 --> 16:18.228
Sandy Rivers
could be anywhere.

16:19.514 --> 16:22.416
And... wrestle!

16:23.985 --> 16:25.569
Hey.

16:25.571 --> 16:28.388
I'm sorry, baby.

16:28.390 --> 16:30.074
I just...
I want our kid

16:30.076 --> 16:32.409
