universe is magical.

16:32.411 --> 16:34.445
You know, like
my dad taught me.

16:34.447 --> 16:36.363
You know what
my dad taught me?

16:36.365 --> 16:38.615
Nothing...
'cause he was never there.

16:40.835 --> 16:44.872
"June 22nd, 1996,
Brooklyn, New York.

16:44.874 --> 16:48.742
"A man misses his daughter's
high school graduation.

16:48.744 --> 16:50.961
"Later, she discovers
her babysitting money

16:50.963 --> 16:52.963
